      "id": "dab185aaf344d084",
      "text": "My work on patterns (mostly on security patterns) as an engineering tool started in 2006. More recently, I worked on the [http://www.secfutur.eu/ SecFutur] project and had the opportunity to advance on this topic. This page is partly based on the results of this project, as well as my personal work, and the collaboration of many colleagues. Although I can't mention all of them here, I want to especially acknowledge the collaboration of Jose Ruiz, Marcos Arjona, Carsten Rudolph, Ed Fernandez, Andrew P. Moore, Bob Hanmer, David Mundie and Ward Cunningham because this page would not be possible without their help and support."
